00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:52.210
in the field of photovoltaics.

00:06:52.210 --> 00:06:55.750
This is not your parents'
solar energy anymore.

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:57.350
Things have changed quite a bit.

00:06:57.350 --> 00:06:59.680
And hopefully, over the
